EXTRACTED VALUE: Never has picking up rubbish felt so good. [Jan 2008, p.92]
Even though most of the modes are all very similar, you'll have a blast rally racing every time you pick this one up!
Mercs 2 is a largely successful effort that will literally give you more "bang" for your buck than most games out there.
A solid test of the player's reflexes mixed with eye-melting visuals make this a title worth more than its weight in Marketplace points.
Dragon Ball Z: Burst Limit is a pretty good game that manages to stay true to the anime series.
